<i>noun</i>: 과단성 [과ː단썽], 결단성 [결딴썽], 결단력 [결딴녁] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>과단성 [과ː단썽]</dt><br>
<dd>decisiveness</dd><br>
<dd>빠르고 단호하게 결정하는 성질.</dd><br>
<dd>The quality of deciding quickly and resolutely.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>결단성 [결딴썽]</dt><br>
<dd>decisiveness</dd><br>
<dd>중요한 일을 판단하여 최종적으로 결정하는 성질.</dd><br>
<dd>A personality trait characterized by aptness at judging what is important and making a final decision.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>결단력 [결딴녁]</dt><br>
<dd>decisiveness; determination</dd><br>
<dd>중요한 일을 판단하여 최종적으로 결정하는 능력.</dd><br>
<dd>The ability to judge what is important and making a final decision.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>